         <div type="translation">
            <ab>In the name of Allah the merciful and compassionate;Removal for Isáaq - - - - and his two sons) for 3 2/3 (1/24) carat 2/3;Three weight measure dinars and two thirds of a carat, and two thirds.;He delivered it to Aámed ibn Jabb��r, the agent of Muáammad ibn ìAêim,;For the khar��j on what he sowed in BarmȦda for the year forty;And two hundred. It was written Wednesday baæunah 25;Year 240 3 2/3 (1/24) carat 2/3</ab>
